{"tid":1865600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣明天起暫停港澳居民入台證申請","createTime":"2020-02-06T09:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T09:14:01.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ac2717176d32aee0673b38216bcf0ec6f29c5c1d","tid":1865600,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:14:01.000Z","msg":"在台灣，陸委會副主委邱垂正宣布，明天凌晨零時起暫停對港澳居民網簽、落地簽及雲端申請入台證之申請。<br />\n<br />\n港澳居民如有急事來台，要提出政府證明，到台灣駐港澳辦事處申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507040-20200206.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507040-20200206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsj%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=2e8e9921\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507040-20200206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2bd28082\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507040-20200206.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}